    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Khi đó: } P(A) = \\frac{1,5x}{1,5x + x} = \\frac{3}{5}; P(\\bar{A}) = 1 - P(A) = \\frac{2}{5}.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
